hopobject.body: What sort of work do you do? methotrexate injection for ectopic pregnancy Those modifications might mean shorter-term deferrals like the temporary bans on people who travel to certain countries, instead of a lifetime ban, said Dr. Robert Makar, associate director of blood transfusion at Massachusetts General Hospital. But donors might still have to refrain from having sex with other men for a certain period of time before they are fully eligible to donate, he said.
